flowchart TD
  Source[External food source] --> Snapshot[Immutable raw snapshot]
  Snapshot --> Validate[Schema and licence validation]
  Validate --> Normalise[Deterministic nutrient normalisation]
  Normalise --> Candidate[Candidate food record]
  Candidate --> Quality[Automated quality checks]
  Quality --> Review[Human or policy review]
  Review --> Canonical[(Canonical food catalogue)]
  Canonical --> Index[Search index]
  Index --> Device[Offline mobile subset]
  Device --> Meal[User meal]
  Meal --> Confirm[User confirmation]
  Confirm --> History[(Private meal history)]
